====================== Swimlanes for QBR goals ==============

issueFunction in linkedIssuesOf
("
    key=ISSUEKEY 
   
") OR
    (
      issueFunction in subtasksOf("type=Story and issuefunction in linkedissuesof(\"key=ISSUEKEY\")")
    )
OR key=ISSUEKEY
OR issuefunction in subtasksOf("key=ISSUEKEY")

============== Filter by Team ==============

Gimme all issues with 
  the label Kortit
  and their subtasks
  and the Features linked to them
  and their subtasks

labels in (kortit) 
OR (issueFunction in subtasksOf("labels in (kortit)"))
OR (issuefunction in linkedissuesof("labels in (kortit)")) 
OR (issuefunction in subtasksOf("issuefunction in linkedissuesof(\"labels in (kortit)\")
                                ")
   )

============== Filter by QBR Goal ==============

QBR Goal = Feature

type = feature OR (issueFunction in subtasksOf("type in (Feature)"))
